 130:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * @brief Universal Serial Interface Channel(USIC) driver for serial communication.
 131:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  *
 132:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * The Universal Serial Interface Channel(USIC) module is a flexible interface module
 133:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * covering several serial communication protocols. A USIC module contains two
 134:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * independent communication channels named USICx_CH0 and USICx_CH1, with x
 135:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * being the number of the USIC module. The user can program, during run-time, which protocol will 
 136:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * by each communication channel and which pins are used.
 137:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * The driver provides APIs, configuration structures and enumerations to configure common features
 138:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * communication protocols.
 139:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  *
 140:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * USIC driver features:
 141:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Allows configuration of FIFO for transmit and receive functions.
 142:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Provides a structure type XMC_USIC_CH_t to represent the USIC channel registers in a programm
 143:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  friendly format.
 144:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Allows configuration of automatic update for frame length, word length, slave select or slave
 145:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Allows transmission of data to FIFO using XMC_USIC_CH_TXFIFO_PutData() and XMC_USIC_CH_TXFIFO
 146:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Allows reading of received data in FIFO using XMC_USIC_CH_RXFIFO_GetData()
 147:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Allows configuration of baudrate using XMC_USIC_CH_SetBaudrate()
 148:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * -# Provides API to trigger interrupts using XMC_USIC_CH_TriggerServiceRequest()
 149:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * @{
 150:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  */
