2053:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Disables the selected interrupt events related to receive FIFO. \n\n
