2055:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * flags from the status register using the API XMC_USIC_CH_RXFIFO_GetEvent().
2056:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Event bitmasks can be constructed using the enumeration \a XMC_USIC_CH_RXFIFO_EVENT_CONF. For pr
2057:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * multiple events, combine the events using bitwise OR operation.
