 347:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * 				   and \a oversampling. Maximum baudrate can be derived using the formula: (fperiph * 1023)/
