 350:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * 					 \b Range: 4 to 32. Value should be chosen based on the protocol used.
 351:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * @return XMC_UART_CH_STATUS_t Status indicating the baudrate configuration.\n
