 465:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * Sets the number of data bits for UART communication.\n\n
 466:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * The frame length is configured by setting the input value to \a SCTR register.
 467:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * The value of \a frame_length will be decremented by 1, before setting it to the register.
 468:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_uart.h ****  * Frame length should not be set to 64 for UART communication.
